metadata.name: Love is Love
metadata.description: Love is Love is more than just a project; it's a movement aimed at spreading a powerful message of acceptance and inclusivity. At its core, this movement reminds us that love knows no bounds, and that it's our duty to be open-minded and celebrate our differences. Love, after all, is patient and kind; it doesn't envy or boast, nor is it arrogant or rude. It doesn't insist on its own way or hold grudges. Instead, love rejoices in the truth, bears all things, believes all things, hopes all things, and endures all things. It transcends nationality, creed, and color, reminding us that we're all united by the power of love. So let's join hands and celebrate love in all its forms â€“ because, as the saying goes, love is love.
